{"tid":1996970,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"5月2號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T02:18:28.000Z","uid":292499,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d175274d312bef39316506c67ede1d2c195693","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 5 月 2 日 星期六】<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕥10:30 <br />\n👤曹(19) #提堂（#1228上水 擾亂公眾秩序涉踢及拉扯途人的行李箱）<br />\n🕦11:30 <br />\n👥李,*(14-27) #提堂（#1123粉嶺 縱火:涉於姚銘區議員辦事處(民建聯)縱火）<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 2 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤葉(20) #提堂（#1001屯門 襲警、管有非法用途工具:涉用雨傘擲向警員曾展鷹；噴漆）"},{"pid":"fd3957cb2b6f6ebcddc92ca04f5a9baed734cb8b","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=e9ca6cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"1ff4c668480cd82461a136d2c1c6515e34972c97","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=152e8abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=645a41d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"4ee124dd2cf4316f3afc01bc34f7f35edaa6136b","tid":1996970,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04c852fbc35b40ca6a0781eebf919dc286bf94d5","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chP36ZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchP36ZO.jpg&h=0e2d89de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf436905404f9a1016154dd35d3c28ff2f9ac7e2","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排<br />\n</strong>- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"19467c3ec467c8b77c5c6fa06551ca01d454d432","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n粉嶺裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界東</strong><br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺法院大樓] **不建議<br />\n上水：79K       [璧峰路]<br />\n打鼓嶺：79K   [粉嶺法院大樓]<br />\n大老山：277X [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界西</strong><br />\n屯門：261       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n青衣：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大欖：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n藍田站、觀塘道、彩虹邨：277X  [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后：673 [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺相對少對外交通，其他地區需使用黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"bf186a9abf5916548c8e295b4e3a4313187f249f","tid":1996970,"uid":330312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d988995997129c5a43b7ac44d3c1dfcfcffd13a0","tid":1996970,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"718377e53d82381c20401a893a4d20c18e111d60","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"【保釋及送車位置】<br />\n<br />\n✵送車位位於法院停車場🅿️<br />\n✵揾唔到就圍住法院兜一圈⭕️<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門<br />\n**唯一送車遮陣出出入入都係同一個位<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"d423d18cd7346dbda106fe08e945f1d3fc7a6dc2","tid":1996970,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d988995997129c5a43b7ac44d3c1dfcfcffd13a0","tid":1996970,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:13:27.000Z","msg":"手足好快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b1c962c4751d820fd5c6c741ae9994cbe631ee","tid":1996970,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 